import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'

const Template4 = () => {
  return (
    <Container className='mt-5'>
        <Row className="justify-content-center">
            <Col md={8}>
                <Card md={8}>
                    i
                </Card>
            </Col>
        </Row>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Template4
